---
title: Presto Bacon, Mushroom and Chicken Breast Linguine with Tenderstem Broccoli and Cheese
description: This Presto Bacon, Mushroom and Chicken Breast Linguine is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF230110_R03_W07_UK_QR2913-31_Main_13_add_low-30e8a8eb.jpg
